subtitle: Land use, zoning, building permits, and long-range planning for Aberdeen's growth.
description: Aberdeen Planning and Community Development — building permits, zoning, land use, and long-range planning. Call (410) 272-1600 ext. 221.
deptPhone: "(410) 272-1600 ext. 221"
